==In popular culture==
* A season 4 episode of the Discovery Channel series &quot;A Haunting&quot;, called &quot;The Awakening&quot;, takes place in Bloomington in 2003.
* The AWE DLC for the 2019 video game Control, a game about paranormal events and items, contains a haunted train supposedly derailed in Bloomington.
* The character Henry Blake from the television show M*A*S*H was from Bloomington.

